    "We break text into words for efficient processing.",
    "• Removing punctuations and numbers: Numbers and punctuations convey no meaningful information content and are thus removed from the input text.",
    "• Lowercase: All the text is converted to lowercase for efficient processing.• Lemmatization: Lemmatization is a text normalization technique used in Natural Language Processing (NLP).",
    "It's used to identify word variations and determine the root of a word.",
    "Lemmatization groups different inflected forms of words into the root form, which have the same meaning."
